
// TM4C123 connected to Nokia 5110 LCD display

// Wiring (using the third SPI port on TM4C123):
// TM4C123 -  LCD 5110        Comment
// ==================================
// VBUS    -  Vcc             My version of 5110 supports 3v to 5v
// VBUS    -  LED             Backlight
// GND     -  GND
// PB_5    -  RST             Reset 
// PB_4    -  SCLK            SCK(2) to Clock
// PB_7    -  DN<MOSI>        MOSI(2) to Serial data in
// PA_7    -  SCE             Chip Select
// PA_2    -  D/C             Select between data or command




